== 轶事 ==
2021年6月，当[[索尼互动娱乐|索尼互动娱乐]]宣布收购芬兰游戏公司{{le|Housemarque|Housemarque}}时，PlayStation日本分公司却放出了收购蓝点游戏的祝贺图片。<ref>[https://www.vg247.com/2021/06/29/playstation-japan-may-accidentally-leaked-bluepoint-games-acquisition/ PlayStation Japan may have accidentally leaked a Bluepoint Games acquisition].VG247.2021-06-29.[2021-07-04].</ref>而在同年9月，索尼正式宣布收购蓝点游戏。<ref>[https://www.polygon.com/22702363/sony-buys-bluepoint-games-sie-playstation-studios Sony acquires Demon’s Souls remake studio Bluepoint Games].Polygon.2021-09-30.[2021-10-01].</ref>

